---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">
      <img
        class="mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-xl rounded-3xl"
        width="576"
        height="864"
        src="/sew.jpg"
        alt="Seamstress Sewing In An Interior by Carl Holsøe (Danish, 1863-1935)"
      />
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
        <!-- Mission description -->
        <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Our mission</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Algomore Tech stands at the intersection of technological innovation and social impact. We're more than just consultants – we're partners in your journey toward digital transformation and community empowerment. Our team combines deep technical expertise with a profound understanding of small business challenges to deliver solutions that make a difference.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              We believe that powerful technology shouldn't be reserved for big corporations. That's why we've made it our mission to bring enterprise-grade solutions to small businesses, solopreneurs, nonprofits, and community organizations at accessible prices. By bridging the digital divide, we help create a more equitable business landscape where everyone has the tools they need to succeed.
            </p>
            <p class="text-primary-950/70 dark:text-primary-200/70 text-base sm:text-lg">
              Our approach goes beyond conventional consulting. We immerse ourselves in your world, understanding your unique challenges and aspirations, to craft solutions that not only solve today's problems but prepare you for tomorrow's opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
